# About this capsule

This capsule is running the openhost-gemini app on an OpenHost compute
space. The code lives at:

=> https://github.com/imbue-openhost/openhost-gemini

## What's serving this

* Agate -- a minimal Rust implementation of the Gemini protocol.
* Running in a Debian slim container.
* Self-signed TLS certificate, auto-generated on first boot.
* Content served from the persistent volume mounted at
  $OPENHOST_APP_DATA_DIR/content inside the container.

